strings: <se_def>Awesome!: what are you doing here Have You Got Drymagus? true or better
<se_def>Awesome!: What kind of wind brought you here?
<se_def>Awesome!: Are you in search of Chand Veena? course name...
<se_def>Awesome!: OK! I heard about it in a book I got from the Ascanthus Empire.
<se_def>Awesome!: Why are you still looking for it? How strange
<se_def>Awesome!: Oh, do you have any moonshine harp? I think I will be very happy for you.
<se_def>Awesome!: We've got to find Dolmagus! Let us always focus on the work ahead.
<se_def>Awesome!: It turns out that there is still a lot of free time.
<se_def>Awesome!: Even if it's a guitar in the moonlight, I don't know what to expect.
<se_def>Awesome!: Why are travelers always foreigners? It went beyond my imagination. But it could be outer space... Hahaha!
<se_def>Awesome!: I'm curious because I read an article about Selenovus' Harp in a book we got from Empire Escanth.
<se_def>Awesome!: But what you're after is very interesting.
